<h1>Privacy Policy for TrillShot</h1>
<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 15, 2025</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>
<p>This app displays advertisements provided by Google AdMob. AdMob may collect and use data to provide personalized ads. For more information about how Google uses data, please visit:</p>
<p><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google Privacy Policy</a></p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<p>Our app collects location data to enable proximity-based features. We collect:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Location information (when app is in use)</li>
    <li>User profile information</li>
    <li>Photos and messages shared within the app</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Google AdMob:</strong> For displaying advertisements</li>
    <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> For backend services and data storage</li>
</ul>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For questions about this privacy policy, contact us at: support@trillshot.com</p>
